OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with some patchy rain or
OL,7,Fdrizzle. Then this afternoon will be
OL,8,Flargely dry with some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells, mainly in the south and east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,13,Flate brightness in places. Then cloudy
OL,14,Fovernight with some patchy rain and
OL,15,Fdrizzle.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FPatchy light rain at first,
OL,18,Fotherwise it will be dry. Starting off
OL,19,Fcloudy but some bright spells in
OL,20,Fplaces by afternoon. Warm in any
OL,21,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
